# Aesthetic library attribution + provenance (AUTH2)
# License compliance + attribution integrity — any change must walk the
# license text, provenance, manifest, or NOTICES path, which all have
# downstream obligations (CC-BY-SA-4.0 ShareAlike, BSD-3 attribution).
assets/aesthetic-library/LICENSE.*              @ryanklee
assets/aesthetic-library/_NOTICES.md            @ryanklee
assets/aesthetic-library/_manifest.yaml         @ryanklee
assets/aesthetic-library/**/provenance.yaml     @ryanklee
